quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  33,69,"Aey logon jo iman laye ho, un logon ki tarah na ban jao jinhon ne Moosa ko aziyatein (ranj pahuncha) di thin, phir Allah ne unki banayi hui baaton se uski baraat farmayi(cleared him) aur woh Allah ke nazdeek ba-izzat tha"
  33,70,"Aey iman laney walon, Allah se daro aur theek baat kiya karo"
  33,71,Allah tumhare aamal durust kardega aur tumhare kasooron se darguzar famayega. Jo shaks Allah aur uske Rasool ki itaat karey usne badi kamiyabi haasil ki
  33,72,"Humne is amanat ko aasmano aur zameen aur pahadon ke saamne pesh kiya to woh usey uthane ke liye tayyar na huey, aur issey darr gaye. Magar Insaan ne isey utha liya, beshak woh bada zaalim aur jahil (ignorant) hai"
  33,73,"Is baar-e-amanat ko uthane ka laazmi nateeja yeh hai ke Allah munafiq mardon aur auraton, aur mushrik mardon aur auraton ko saza dey aur momin mardon aur auraton ki towbah qabool karey.Allah darguzar farmane wala aur raheem hai"